-I realize this was implemented as an improvement, but it's quite frustrating that now, every time I click a bar in the schedule view to inspect it's date range, or to find it in the scope listing, the item's detail view is shown. Typically, I'm clicking the bar to navigate between the various items to review estimates or team assignments ... not to read the summary or description. I would suggest changing the behavior to simply bring the scope item into view and highlight it ... then creating another mechanism to invoke the detail view. OR provide this as a plan setting ... letting the user choose their preferred behavior.-

